The used muograph is a multilayered gaseous tracker designed for field measurements, it is composed of 8 Close Cathode Chambers74 with a surface area about 40 × 40 cm2 placed equidistantly 40-40 mm apart (illustrated in Fig. 15). Data acquisition and power system are made of costum boards controlled by a RaspberryPi microcomputer, allowing a simple user interface (e.g. via a mobile phone) for managing measurements. The full system is encapsulated in a box of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
